Package net.runelite.client.plugins.fps

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FpsConfig  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FpsDrawListener
    FPS Draw Listener runs after the canvas has been painted with the buffered image (unused in this plugin) It specifically is designed only to pause when RS decides to paint the canvas, after the canvas has been painted.
    FpsOverlay
    The built in FPS overlay has a few problems that this one does not have, most of all: it is distracting.
    FpsPlugin
    FPS Control has two primary areas, this plugin class just keeps those areas up to date and handles setup / teardown.
